Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.07,0:02:51.61,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}不要抹去心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.53,0:02:54.24,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}不要獨自哭泣
